author: @blarmy827
text: Damn it Tae! Stayed longer in front and f the camera and we barely got to see the last member jungkookies face and expression 😂 I know you love the camera babe but sharing is caring 😘 all 7 of f them look absolutely incredible…. And I don’t know why but it’s cute to me that the rappers have blondish or super light colored hair and the vocalists have dark hair… I couldn’t tell exactly but does nobody have vibrant colored hair? Interesting! Anyway love them all and wait they’re performing at the vmas? I was low key kinda disappointed with the remix. Her verse was pretty cool and I liked that she had some ad libs throughout the song… but I duno I always hope that the boys parts will be extended or a little different for their remixes… bc nothing changes for them… just her part laid on top of theirs… just feels like they could do so much more make it a true remix… like the steve aoki remix of mic drop has way more English and the heat has more of a kick to it… you can hear more changes… stuff like this remix feels rushed IMO…. But regardless I hope they have a safe trip… get to enjoy themselves and finally be coming back to America… if they somehow find their way down to LA for something … I don’t even want to think about it. Congrats bts on legit being so far above the bar that they will never catch you! Enjoy yourselves boys even with the work… you deserve it and so much more!!!

text:
BTS until 2019 was genuine but now they are losing they real essence because of an award.
Because now they are talking another way  singing full letters in English, calling the attention of americans, all because of the Grammy as if the award was more important than anything... but for what? 

BTS conquered many things, had greater acknowledge, gained more respect and countless numbers of fans and awards. 

BTS, be yourself, be korean, sing in Korean and keep your real essence.
That way you'll get the Grammy you deserve. 

That is what K-pop is all about.
